  "texts": [
    "Overall, these cameras allowed for a detailed and accurate analysis of the participant's performance during badminton strokes.",
    "Survey data.",
    "In addition to collecting sensor data, we also gathered survey data on the physical attributes of the participants, periods of badminton training, and their experience with wearing sensors.",
    "We gathered fundamental metadata such as age, and gender, as well as biometrics such as weight, height, joint length, and dominant limbs from the participants.",
    "Furthermore, we obtained information on the duration of their professional training and their self-reported level of expertise to assess their skill levels."
  ]
